{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "premium-guide-em5qfy7ev-k",
    "category": "pro/premium_guide",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=em5QfY7EV_k",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm, so tired. I need more coffee.",
      "zh": "嗯，好累。我需要更多咖啡。",
      "ja": "うーん、疲れた。もっとコーヒーが必要だ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The soup, it is boiling. This will be perfect for lunch. I will let it cook slowly.",
      "zh": "湯正在沸騰。這將是完美的午餐。我會讓它慢慢煮。",
      "ja": "スープが沸騰している。ランチにぴったりだ。ゆっくり煮込もう。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no, what is that sound?",
      "zh": "哦不，那是什麼聲音？",
      "ja": "ああ、何の音？",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The garbage truck, it is coming!",
      "zh": "垃圾車來了！",
      "ja": "ゴミ収集車が来てる！",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I forgot! I forgot to take out the trash!",
      "zh": "我忘了！我忘了倒垃圾！",
      "ja": "忘れた！ゴミを出すのを忘れた！",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The bins! They are still by the garage. I didn't put them out.",
      "zh": "垃圾桶還在車庫旁。我沒把它們拿出去。",
      "ja": "ゴミ箱がまだガレージのそばにある。出してなかった。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No time must rush. Rush means run fast.",
      "zh": "沒時間了，必須快點。快點就是跑得快。",
      "ja": "時間がない、急がなきゃ。急ぐって速く走るってこと。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh? Snow? Wait, what?",
      "zh": "咦？下雪了？等等，什麼？",
      "ja": "え？雪？ちょっと、何？",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So cold this jacket it is thin. Very thin.",
      "zh": "這件外套好薄，好冷。非常薄。",
      "ja": "このジャケット薄い。とても薄い。寒い。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not warm enough, but no time.",
      "zh": "不夠暖和，但沒時間了。",
      "ja": "暖かくないけど、時間がない。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, wait for me!",
      "zh": "嘿，等等我！",
      "ja": "ねえ、待って！",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please stop!",
      "zh": "請停下！",
      "ja": "止まって！",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, I missed it.",
      "zh": "不，我錯過了。",
      "ja": "ダメ、逃した。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Gone, the truck is gone too late.",
      "zh": "走了，垃圾車走了，太晚了。",
      "ja": "行っちゃった、ゴミ収集車が行っちゃった。遅すぎた。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I must pull this back all the way home in this cold.",
      "zh": "現在我必須在這寒冷中把它拉回家。",
      "ja": "今からこれを寒い中、家まで引き返さなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So cold, I am freezing.",
      "zh": "好冷，我快凍僵了。",
      "ja": "寒い、凍えそう。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Freezing! Very, very cold. My body is shaking.",
      "zh": "快凍僵了！非常非常冷。我的身體在顫抖。",
      "ja": "凍えてる！とても、とても寒い。体が震えてる。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally done.",
      "zh": "終於完成了。",
      "ja": "やっと終わった。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now inside, get warm.",
      "zh": "現在進去，暖和一下。",
      "ja": "さあ中に入って暖まろう。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, the keys.",
      "zh": "等等，鑰匙。",
      "ja": "待って、鍵。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "zh": "不，不，不，不。",
      "ja": "いや、いや、いや、いや。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where are my keys? Where are my keys?",
      "zh": "我的鑰匙在哪裡？我的鑰匙在哪裡？",
      "ja": "鍵はどこ？鍵はどこ？",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The door, it is locked. I am locked out, locked out!",
      "zh": "門鎖著。我被鎖在外面了，鎖在外面了！",
      "ja": "ドアが閉まってる。外に閉め出された、閉め出された！",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Locked out, I cannot get inside.",
      "zh": "被鎖在外面，我進不去。",
      "ja": "閉め出されて、中に入れない。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Keys are inside, I am outside.",
      "zh": "鑰匙在裡面，我在外面。",
      "ja": "鍵は中、私は外。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, the soup! The soup, I left it on the stove!",
      "zh": "等等，湯！湯，我放在爐子上了！",
      "ja": "待って、スープ！スープをコンロに置きっぱなし！",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The stove! I can see the stove!",
      "zh": "爐子！我看到爐子了！",
      "ja": "コンロ！コンロが見える！",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Still on, the soup is boiling.",
      "zh": "還開著，湯還在煮。",
      "ja": "まだついてる、スープが沸騰してる。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If it burns, smoke, maybe fire.",
      "zh": "如果燒焦，會冒煙，可能會起火。",
      "ja": "焦げたら煙が出て、火事になるかも。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is an emergency. A very big problem.",
      "zh": "這是緊急狀況。一個很大的問題。",
      "ja": "これは緊急事態。とても大きな問題だ。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ring ring, but nobody responds.",
      "zh": "叮咚叮咚，但沒有人回應。",
      "ja": "チャイムが鳴るけど誰も出ない。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Respond means answer. Come to the door.",
      "zh": "回應就是回答。來開門。",
      "ja": "返事するって答えること。ドアに来ること。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But nobody comes.",
      "zh": "但沒有人來。",
      "ja": "でも誰も来ない。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, take that! Go, go, go!",
      "zh": "是的，接招！快，快，快！",
      "ja": "よし、これを受け取れ！行け、行け、行け！",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Family day, no school, warm bed, this is the life.",
      "zh": "家庭日，沒上學，溫暖的床，這就是生活。",
      "ja": "家族の日、学校なし、暖かいベッド、これが人生だ。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So cold outside.",
      "zh": "外面好冷。",
      "ja": "外はとても寒い。",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack, Emma, open the door!",
      "zh": "Jack，Emma，開門！",
      "ja": "ジャック、エマ、ドアを開けて！",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They have headphones on their ears.",
      "zh": "他們戴著耳機。",
      "ja": "彼らはイヤホンをつけている。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They cannot hear me, they are distracted.",
      "zh": "他們聽不到我，他們分心了。",
      "ja": "私の声が聞こえない、気が散っている。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, new plan.",
      "zh": "好，新的計劃。",
      "ja": "よし、新しい作戦だ。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Snowballs, I will make snowballs.",
      "zh": "雪球，我要做雪球。",
      "ja": "雪玉を作る。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will aim at Jack's window.",
      "zh": "我要瞄準Jack的窗戶。",
      "ja": "ジャックの窓を狙う。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Aim, point here, throw there.",
      "zh": "瞄準，指向這裡，投擲那裡。",
      "ja": "狙いを定めて、ここを指して、あそこに投げる。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, right on target.",
      "zh": "是的，正中目標。",
      "ja": "よし、的中。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's going to be fun to clean up.",
      "zh": "這清理起來會很有趣。",
      "ja": "これを片付けるのは大変そう。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, keep going.",
      "zh": "是的，繼續。",
      "ja": "うん、続けて。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So close now.",
      "zh": "現在很接近了。",
      "ja": "もうすぐだ。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing, he doesn't see it.",
      "zh": "沒反應，他沒看到。",
      "ja": "何もない、彼は見ていない。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He is distracted.",
      "zh": "他分心了。",
      "ja": "彼は気が散っている。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Looking at his game, not at me.",
      "zh": "看著他的遊戲，不看我。",
      "ja": "ゲームを見ていて、私を見ていない。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One more try, Emma's window.",
      "zh": "再試一次，Emma的窗戶。",
      "ja": "もう一回、エマの窓。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My hands so cold, I cannot feel them.",
      "zh": "我的手好冷，感覺不到了。",
      "ja": "手がすごく冷たくて、感覚がない。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bullseye!",
      "zh": "正中紅心！",
      "ja": "ど真ん中！",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Heh, that was fun.",
      "zh": "呵，那很有趣。",
      "ja": "へへ、楽しかった。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Heh, that's so funny.",
      "zh": "呵，真好笑。",
      "ja": "へへ、面白い。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, much better.",
      "zh": "啊，好多了。",
      "ja": "ああ、ずっといい。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nom, my fingers are nom.",
      "zh": "嗯，我的手指麻木了。",
      "ja": "うーん、指がしびれてる。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nom, I touch them, I feel nothing.",
      "zh": "嗯，我摸它們，什麼感覺都沒有。",
      "ja": "うーん、触っても何も感じない。",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, a ladder.",
      "zh": "等等，一個梯子。",
      "ja": "待って、はしごだ。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A ladder has steps, I can climb up, go higher.",
      "zh": "梯子有階梯，我可以爬上去，更高。",
      "ja": "はしごには段がある、登って高く行ける。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Heavy, so heavy.",
      "zh": "重，好重。",
      "ja": "重い、とても重い。",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I must try.",
      "zh": "但我必須試試。",
      "ja": "でもやらなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, I can do this.",
      "zh": "好，我能做到。",
      "ja": "よし、できる。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One step.",
      "zh": "一步。",
      "ja": "一歩。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Two steps.",
      "zh": "兩步。",
      "ja": "二歩。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Three steps.",
      "zh": "三步。",
      "ja": "三歩。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Four steps.",
      "zh": "四步。",
      "ja": "四歩。",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Almost there, keep going.",
      "zh": "快到了，繼續。",
      "ja": "もう少し、続けて。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no, so much snow.",
      "zh": "哦不，雪好多。",
      "ja": "ああ、雪がいっぱい。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa, it's sliding everywhere.",
      "zh": "哇，到處都滑。",
      "ja": "うわ、どこも滑ってる。",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is slippery.",
      "zh": "很滑。",
      "ja": "滑りやすい。",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Slippery, my hand slides, like ice.",
      "zh": "滑，我的手滑動，就像冰一樣。",
      "ja": "滑る、手が滑る、氷みたい。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not safe.",
      "zh": "不安全。",
      "ja": "危なくない。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Too dangerous, too slippery.",
      "zh": "太危險了，太滑了。",
      "ja": "危険すぎる、滑りすぎる。",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I cannot do this.",
      "zh": "我做不到。",
      "ja": "できない。",
      "time": "00:06:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need another way.",
      "zh": "我需要另一條路。",
      "ja": "別の方法が必要だ。",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What can I do?",
      "zh": "我能做什麼？",
      "ja": "どうすればいい？",
      "time": "00:06:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nobody hears me, I am so cold.",
      "zh": "沒有人聽到我，我好冷。",
      "ja": "誰も聞こえない、すごく寒い。",
      "time": "00:06:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Family day, I hope they like lemon cake.",
      "zh": "家庭日，希望他們喜歡檸檬蛋糕。",
      "ja": "家族の日、レモンケーキが気に入るといいな。",
      "time": "00:06:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This cake should bring some cheer to the neighbors.",
      "zh": "這蛋糕應該能帶給鄰居一些歡樂。",
      "ja": "このケーキは近所の人に喜びをもたらすはず。",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Careful now, don't want to slip on this lovely snow.",
      "zh": "小心點，不想在這美麗的雪地滑倒。",
      "ja": "気をつけて、この素敵な雪で滑りたくない。",
      "time": "00:06:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "あれは何？",
      "time": "00:06:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is someone Anna?",
      "zh": "是Anna嗎？",
      "ja": "誰か、アンナ？",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mrs. Peterson?",
      "zh": "Peterson太太？",
      "ja": "ピーターソンさん？",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna, what are you doing out here?",
      "zh": "Anna，你在這裡做什麼？",
      "ja": "アンナ、ここで何してるの？",
      "time": "00:07:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh my goodness, you are freezing.",
      "zh": "天啊，你快凍僵了。",
      "ja": "まあ、大変、凍えてる。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am locked out, locked out how long.",
      "zh": "我被鎖在外面，被鎖多久了。",
      "ja": "閉め出された、どれくらい？",
      "time": "00:07:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Almost one hour, come up right now.",
      "zh": "快一小時了，現在上來吧。",
      "ja": "もうすぐ1時間、すぐ上がって。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You need to get warm.",
      "zh": "你需要暖和一下。",
      "ja": "暖まらないと。",
      "time": "00:07:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sit here, right here.",
      "zh": "坐這裡，就這裡。",
      "ja": "ここに座って、ここ。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:07:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There you go.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "はい、どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How did this happen?",
      "zh": "這是怎麼發生的？",
      "ja": "どうしてこうなったの？",
      "time": "00:07:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I took out the trash.",
      "zh": "我去倒垃圾了。",
      "ja": "ゴミを出したの。",
      "time": "00:07:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I forgot my keys.",
      "zh": "我忘了帶鑰匙。",
      "ja": "鍵を忘れたの。",
      "time": "00:07:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh dear, I will make tea, hot tea.",
      "zh": "哦親愛的，我來泡茶，熱茶。",
      "ja": "あらまあ、お茶を入れるわ、熱いお茶。",
      "time": "00:07:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right, let's get this started.",
      "zh": "好，開始吧。",
      "ja": "よし、始めよう。",
      "time": "00:07:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There we go, nice and hot.",
      "zh": "好了，熱騰騰的。",
      "ja": "はい、熱々だ。",
      "time": "00:07:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Careful now, pouring the water.",
      "zh": "小心倒水。",
      "ja": "気をつけて、水を注ぐ。",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There, a perfect cup.",
      "zh": "好了，一杯完美的茶。",
      "ja": "はい、完璧な一杯。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, this feels so good.",
      "zh": "喔，這感覺真好。",
      "ja": "ああ、気持ちいい。",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mrs. Peterson, can I use your phone?",
      "zh": "Peterson太太，我可以用你的電話嗎？",
      "ja": "ピーターソンさん、電話を使ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Of course dear.",
      "zh": "當然可以，親愛的。",
      "ja": "もちろんよ、あなた。",
      "time": "00:08:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Michael, it's me, again.",
      "zh": "Michael，是我，又是我。",
      "ja": "マイケル、また私よ。",
      "time": "00:08:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am at Mrs. Peterson's house.",
      "zh": "我在Peterson太太家。",
      "ja": "ピーターソンさんの家にいる。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please call back.",
      "zh": "請回電。",
      "ja": "折り返し電話して。",
      "time": "00:08:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No answer, again.",
      "zh": "又沒接。",
      "ja": "また出ない。",
      "time": "00:08:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is he at work?",
      "zh": "他在工作嗎？",
      "ja": "彼は仕事中？",
      "time": "00:08:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He should be, but my kids are home.",
      "zh": "他應該在，但我的孩子們在家。",
      "ja": "そうのはずだけど、子供たちは家にいる。",
      "time": "00:08:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They cannot hear the doorbell?",
      "zh": "他們聽不到門鈴聲嗎？",
      "ja": "ドアベルの音が聞こえないの？",
      "time": "00:08:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They wear headphones, always headphones.",
      "zh": "他們戴著耳機，總是戴著耳機。",
      "ja": "いつもイヤホンをつけている。",
      "time": "00:08:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Gaming, music, they hear nothing.",
      "zh": "玩遊戲，聽音樂，他們什麼也聽不到。",
      "ja": "ゲームや音楽で、何も聞こえない。",
      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I tried everything, doorbell, snowballs.",
      "zh": "我試過所有方法，門鈴，雪球。",
      "ja": "ドアベルも雪玉も試した。",
      "time": "00:08:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh dear, that's a challenge.",
      "zh": "哦親愛的，這真是個挑戰。",
      "ja": "あらまあ、大変ね。",
      "time": "00:08:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Headphones, oh I understand this.",
      "zh": "耳機，哦，我懂了。",
      "ja": "イヤホンか、わかるわ。",
      "time": "00:08:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yesterday our Wi-Fi stopped.",
      "zh": "昨天我們的Wi-Fi斷了。",
      "ja": "昨日Wi-Fiが止まった。",
      "time": "00:08:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My grandson lives with me.",
      "zh": "我孫子和我住在一起。",
      "ja": "孫が私と一緒に住んでいる。",
      "time": "00:09:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tyler was upstairs.",
      "zh": "Tyler在樓上。",
      "ja": "タイラーは上の階にいた。",
      "time": "00:09:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Headphones on.",
      "zh": "戴著耳機。",
      "ja": "イヤホンをつけて。",
      "time": "00:09:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But when Wi-Fi stopped.",
      "zh": "但當Wi-Fi斷了。",
      "ja": "でもWi-Fiが止まった時。",
      "time": "00:09:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, he ran down so fast.",
      "zh": "哦，他跑下樓很快。",
      "ja": "ああ、彼はすごく速く降りてきた。",
      "time": "00:09:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No way.",
      "zh": "不可能。",
      "ja": "まさか。",
      "time": "00:09:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like the house was on fire.",
      "zh": "就像房子著火了一樣。",
      "ja": "家が火事みたいに。",
      "time": "00:09:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He came running for Wi-Fi?",
      "zh": "他跑來找Wi-Fi？",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiのために走ってきた？",
      "time": "00:09:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh yes, very fast.",
      "zh": "哦，是的，非常快。",
      "ja": "ああ、すごく速かった。",
      "time": "00:09:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No Wi-Fi is emergency for teenagers.",
      "zh": "沒有Wi-Fi對青少年来說是緊急狀況。",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiがないのはティーンにとって緊急事態。",
      "time": "00:09:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wi-Fi.",
      "zh": "Wi-Fi。",
      "ja": "Wi-Fi。",
      "time": "00:09:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No Wi-Fi they came running.",
      "zh": "沒有Wi-Fi他們就跑過來了。",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiがないと走ってきた。",
      "time": "00:09:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mrs. Peterson, where is your cable box?",
      "zh": "Peterson太太，你的網路盒在哪裡？",
      "ja": "ピーターソンさん、ケーブルボックスはどこ？",
      "time": "00:09:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Cable box?",
      "zh": "網路盒？",
      "ja": "ケーブルボックス？",
      "time": "00:09:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The box outside for internet.",
      "zh": "外面的網路盒。",
      "ja": "外にあるインターネットの箱。",
      "time": "00:09:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "On the side wall.",
      "zh": "在側牆上。",
      "ja": "側面の壁に。",
      "time": "00:09:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:09:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you so much for everything.",
      "zh": "非常感謝你的一切。",
      "ja": "色々ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:09:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "zh": "你要去哪裡？",
      "ja": "どこに行くの？",
      "time": "00:09:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have an idea.",
      "zh": "我有個主意。",
      "ja": "アイデアがある。",
      "time": "00:09:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A desperate idea.",
      "zh": "一個絕望的主意。",
      "ja": "絶望的なアイデア。",
      "time": "00:09:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why-Fi?",
      "zh": "為什麼Wi-Fi？",
      "ja": "なぜWi-Fi？",
      "time": "00:10:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They need Wi-Fi.",
      "zh": "他們需要Wi-Fi。",
      "ja": "彼らはWi-Fiが必要。",
      "time": "00:10:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No Wi-Fi?",
      "zh": "沒有Wi-Fi？",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiなし？",
      "time": "00:10:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They will notice.",
      "zh": "他們會注意到的。",
      "ja": "気づくはず。",
      "time": "00:10:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The cable box.",
      "zh": "網路盒。",
      "ja": "ケーブルボックス。",
      "time": "00:10:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where is it?",
      "zh": "它在哪裡？",
      "ja": "どこ？",
      "time": "00:10:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It must be on the wall somewhere.",
      "zh": "它一定在牆上某處。",
      "ja": "どこか壁にあるはず。",
      "time": "00:10:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is it.",
      "zh": "就是這個。",
      "ja": "これだ。",
      "time": "00:10:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The cable box.",
      "zh": "網路盒。",
      "ja": "ケーブルボックス。",
      "time": "00:10:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The internet box.",
      "zh": "網路盒。",
      "ja": "インターネットの箱。",
      "time": "00:10:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is the cable box.",
      "zh": "這就是網路盒。",
      "ja": "これがケーブルボックス。",
      "time": "00:10:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This brings internet to the house.",
      "zh": "這把網路帶進家裡。",
      "ja": "これが家にインターネットをもたらす。",
      "time": "00:10:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If I disconnect this,",
      "zh": "如果我拔掉它，",
      "ja": "これを切断したら、",
      "time": "00:10:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "the internet will stop.",
      "zh": "網路就會斷掉。",
      "ja": "インターネットが止まる。",
      "time": "00:10:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I have no choice.",
      "zh": "但我別無選擇。",
      "ja": "でも仕方がない。",
      "time": "00:10:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am desperate, very desperate.",
      "zh": "我很絕望，非常絕望。",
      "ja": "絶望的だ、とても絶望的。",
      "time": "00:10:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry kids.",
      "zh": "抱歉孩子們。",
      "ja": "ごめんね、子供たち。",
      "time": "00:10:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Three, two, one.",
      "zh": "三、二、一。",
      "ja": "3、2、1。",
      "time": "00:11:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Done.",
      "zh": "完成。",
      "ja": "完了。",
      "time": "00:11:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I wait.",
      "zh": "現在我等待。",
      "ja": "今は待つ。",
      "time": "00:11:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Will they notice?",
      "zh": "他們會注意到嗎？",
      "ja": "気づくかな？",
      "time": "00:11:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, what?",
      "zh": "不，什麼？",
      "ja": "え？何？",
      "time": "00:11:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The Wi-Fi, it's down.",
      "zh": "Wi-Fi斷了。",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiが切れた。",
      "time": "00:11:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They noticed.",
      "zh": "他們注意到了。",
      "ja": "気づいた。",
      "time": "00:11:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The router, check the router.",
      "zh": "路由器，檢查路由器。",
      "ja": "ルーター、ルーターをチェック。",
      "time": "00:11:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This can't be happening.",
      "zh": "這不可能發生。",
      "ja": "こんなことありえない。",
      "time": "00:11:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What happened?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "何があったの？",
      "time": "00:11:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is the Wi-Fi down?",
      "zh": "Wi-Fi斷了嗎？",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiが切れたの？",
      "time": "00:11:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack, Emma, wait.",
      "zh": "Jack，Emma，等等。",
      "ja": "ジャック、エマ、待って。",
      "time": "00:11:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "zh": "你們在做什麼？",
      "ja": "何してるの？",
      "time": "00:11:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad?",
      "zh": "爸爸？",
      "ja": "パパ？",
      "time": "00:11:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, you're home?",
      "zh": "爸爸，你回家了？",
      "ja": "パパ、家にいるの？",
      "time": "00:11:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We thought you went to work.",
      "zh": "我們以為你去上班了。",
      "ja": "仕事に行ったと思ってた。",
      "time": "00:12:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The Wi-Fi is down.",
      "zh": "Wi-Fi斷了。",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiが切れてる。",
      "time": "00:12:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The router looks fine.",
      "zh": "路由器看起來沒問題。",
      "ja": "ルーターは問題なさそう。",
      "time": "00:12:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Something happened outside.",
      "zh": "外面發生了什麼事。",
      "ja": "外で何かあった。",
      "time": "00:12:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is Dad home?",
      "zh": "為什麼爸爸在家？",
      "ja": "なぜパパが家にいるの？",
      "time": "00:12:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna?",
      "zh": "Anna？",
      "ja": "アンナ？",
      "time": "00:12:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello family.",
      "zh": "哈囉，家人們。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、家族。",
      "time": "00:12:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I disconnected your internet.",
      "zh": "我拔掉了你們的網路。",
      "ja": "インターネットを切断した。",
      "time": "00:12:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna, you're freezing.",
      "zh": "Anna，你快凍僵了。",
      "ja": "アンナ、凍えてるよ。",
      "time": "00:12:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh my god, how long?",
      "zh": "天啊，多久了？",
      "ja": "なんてこった、どれくらい？",
      "time": "00:12:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, you're blue.",
      "zh": "媽媽，你臉色發青。",
      "ja": "ママ、顔色が青いよ。",
      "time": "00:12:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get inside, you're like ice.",
      "zh": "進去吧，你像冰一樣。",
      "ja": "中に入って、氷みたいだよ。",
      "time": "00:12:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was locked out.",
      "zh": "我被鎖在外面。",
      "ja": "閉め出されたの。",
      "time": "00:12:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I tried everything.",
      "zh": "我試了所有方法。",
      "ja": "色々試した。",
      "time": "00:12:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Doorbell, snowballs.",
      "zh": "門鈴，雪球。",
      "ja": "ドアベル、雪玉。",
      "time": "00:12:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Michael?",
      "zh": "Michael？",
      "ja": "マイケル？",
      "time": "00:12:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes?",
      "zh": "是的？",
      "ja": "はい？",
      "time": "00:12:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You are here in the house.",
      "zh": "你在家裡。",
      "ja": "家にいるのね。",
      "time": "00:12:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought you went to work.",
      "zh": "我以為你去上班了。",
      "ja": "仕事に行ったと思ってた。",
      "time": "00:13:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I, uh, I was downstairs.",
      "zh": "我，呃，我在樓下。",
      "ja": "えっと、下の階にいた。",
      "time": "00:13:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Downstairs?",
      "zh": "樓下？",
      "ja": "下の階？",
      "time": "00:13:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "With the remote?",
      "zh": "拿著遙控器？",
      "ja": "リモコン持って？",
      "time": "00:13:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You were home?",
      "zh": "你在家？",
      "ja": "家にいたの？",
      "time": "00:13:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You did not go to work?",
      "zh": "你沒去上班？",
      "ja": "仕事に行かなかったの？",
      "time": "00:13:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can explain.",
      "zh": "我可以解釋。",
      "ja": "説明できる。",
      "time": "00:13:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
